    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It's in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I've honestly babied it since the day I brought it home. It looks and drives just like it did when it first rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, and the interior is spotless. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
