    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade masterpiece that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, the dash is flawless, and all electronics function with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a comprehensive, documented service history and recent preventative maintenance. Every seal is dry, the engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, and the drive is as tight and responsive as the day it was first delivered. Included are the original window sticker, all factory manuals, two sets of keys, and custom-fitted floor mats. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a truly preserved example that satisfies even the most discerning inspection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
