    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously cleaned, and it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you've been looking for that perfect, 'good-as-new' ride without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019d love for this beauty to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
